Command-line interface and argument parsing.

{1 Synopsis}

This module implements the command-line interface for the shibboleth converter
using Cmdliner. It handles argument parsing, option validation, and invocation
of the conversion pipeline.

{1 Features}

- Input/output file path specification
- Verbosity level control
- Conversion flag configuration from command-line options
- Help text and usage information

